==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: pack rat
<hw>pack rat</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Any of several bushy-tailed rodents of the genus <gen>Neotoma</gen>
of western North America, especially <spn>Neotoma cinerea</spn>, which
hoard food and other objects in their nests.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> trade rat, bushytail woodrat, <spn>Neotoma
cinerea</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who habitually saves items, even those
unlikely to be useful.</def> <mark>[Informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>packsaddle</ent>⟦br⟧
